info.alfheimr.book.landing: The first and only known printed copy.$(br2)The book covers all things needed to know about Alfheimr.
info.atlantis.book.landing: The only recorded book on Atlantis but was lost before it could make it to print.$(br2)This book covers all the mystories of the world atlantis.
info.book_on_dragons.book.landing: This book is written by Gavin Young.The worlds leading researcher in everything about dragons. Both in known knowladge and legends.
info.lostworlds.book.landing: A journal written by a mad man talking about the possibilities of different worlds.$(br2)Discovering the mysteries of the many different worlds lost to history.
info.nidavellir.book.landing: Popular edition for all dwarves.$(br2)A basic guide to Nidavellir that all the dwarves carry before entering the mines.
info.skyopia.book.landing: A journal written by the most infamous and notorious pirate in all of Skyopia.$(br2)A survivors guide to the many lands and wild life of Skyopia
info.underworld.book.landing: This book is written by the lord of the underworld hades.$(br2)The reason for this book is to pass on information and knowladge on how to live in the underworld.
